description: A ruby-eyed grinning skull hangs on one of the plain wooden walls, and a mistwood beam ceiling rises overhead.  A sharp wooden guilotine sits in one corner of a speckled black marble floor.  There is a gilded maple cabinet on one side of the shop and a bloodstained marble slab on the other.
